{"tid":1472562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"臥底香港機場深圳公安身分曝光 中国網路刪文滅跡","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:49:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"24c01e28cb4fad8c1588c5eeb1029b7c8d18d529","tid":1472562,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"環球時報「記者」付國豪昨（13）於香港機場受傷的新聞，被中國媒體集中報導，中國官方對此也有發出強烈譴責，相較另一名在機場被綑綁圍毆的中國「遊客」，中媒一概不提徐的姓名身分，僅以「內地遊客」作為代稱。（圖擷取自Twitter「Williams Wang@palato」）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕環球時報記者付國豪昨（13日）於香港機場受傷的新聞，被中國媒體大肆報導，中國官方對此也發出強烈譴責，相較之下，另一名在機場被綑綁圍毆的中國「遊客」卻始終避談，經查證後確認，該中國遊客的真實身份為深圳市公安局福田分局輔警徐錦煬，奇怪的是中媒一概不提徐的姓名身分，僅以「內地遊客」作為代稱，因此遭到許多網友懷疑是「真臥底」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《中央社》報導，徐錦煬昨晚在香港機場遭示威者圍堵，並當場被網路肉搜出真實身分，但徐不僅堅決否認，還自稱只是到機場送機，示威者翻查手機時還發現，徐被捉住便立刻被一個微信群組踢出，之後中國網友在微博上Tag「徐錦煬」，都明顯遭網管刪除。<br />\n<br />\n根據微博顯示，關於「徐錦煬」的討論僅1.4萬次，透過中國百度、搜狗，都搜尋不到「徐錦煬」任何一筆資料，疑似已經被網管「和諧」，但Google上卻可見徐錦煬的新聞與資料，包括其深圳公安局輔警錄取名單的圖片。部分中國網友質疑，徐錦煬昨晚（13）為何會出現在香港機場，但相關發文後來都遭檢舉消失，還有中國網友指出，徐錦煬可能是臥底身分曝光，因此遭中國官媒隱名。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/HsinchuCity/breakingnews/2884685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2FHsinchuCity%2Fbreakingnews%2F2884685&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=429a7fba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2FHsinchuCity%2Fbreakingnews%2F2884685&h=43555381\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/HsinchuCity/breakingnews/2884685</a>"},{"pid":"76db6ac4e55a738e1d326d24e3224cf5f10f2c14","tid":1472562,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EfuFsm3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEfuFsm3.jpg&h=07b60179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QJDfgfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQJDfgfo.jpg&h=f6e5ec7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa888d9f2307db3c3bc192462c990c2034e7ca46","tid":1472562,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警配合<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中共國安特務(付國豪)</span>做大龍鳳，佢嘅任務就係<br />\n「鏡頭前展示俾示威者打到傷晒」，<br />\n國際記者影晒相，<br />\n用國際輿論同全國上下媒體大肆造謠，<br />\n指責示威者打記者/遊客，<br />\n跟住黑警先護送國安特務離開機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">條人渣絕對唔係記者！！！！！！<br />\n之前<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣黑夜斬人恐襲佢都有份參與</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kdK7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kdK7K.jpg&h=8672802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv9iuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv9iuk.jpg&h=da06f494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66bfa39f22cc8d88e369fb9d9b51b3528e4e0b64","tid":1472562,"uid":138116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc200439532430d8d0e65b2f5b98b8f836415bc","tid":1472562,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"人多先捉到，聽日記者再追問下狗狗"}]}